{"id":610863,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/05/香港电台网站-李文足：录像中王全璋苍老呆滞/","date":"2019-05-21T20:19:02Z","modified":"2019-05-21T20:19:02Z","title":"香港电台网站| 李文足：录像中王全璋苍老呆滞","content":"<p>李文足：狱方播放片段片中王全璋苍老呆滞<br />\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-610864\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/mfile_1458494_1_L_20190520222231.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/mfile_1458494_1_L_20190520222231.jpg 1280w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/mfile_1458494_1_L_20190520222231-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/mfile_1458494_1_L_20190520222231-768x576.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/mfile_1458494_1_L_20190520222231-1024x768.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /><br />\n李文足表示很担心丈夫的身心状况。（港台图片）</p>\n<p><span class=\"text_exposed_show\"><br />\n内地维权律师王全璋的太太李文足表示，早上到山东临沂监狱未能成功探望丈夫，监狱的领导播放一段3分钟的片段，是自2015年王全璋在709事件被捕后的首次。</span></p>\n<div class=\"text_exposed_show\">\n<p>她形容，片段中王全璋容颜苍老，神情呆滞，反应迟钝，说话时眼神飘忽，上一句话说完后，要想一段时间后，才能说出来下一句，与当年维权律师李和平和李春富被释放的情况相似，李文足表示，很担心丈夫的身心状况。</p>\n<p>李文足发表声明，表示共四次到监狱，要求与丈夫见面，但前三次监狱领导都以会见室装修为理由，不安排会见，直到今早再到监狱时，才将提前录制好的王全璋片段播放给她看。</p>\n<p>李文足重申，不亲自会见到王全璋，绝不罢休，又指依照法律规定，王全璋到临沂监狱服刑后，可安排会见家属。</p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-610865\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/Capture-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"573\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/Capture-2.png 491w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/05/Capture-2-262x300.png 262w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p>\n<p><strong>中国数字空间 | <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/%E7%8E%8B%E5%85%A8%E7%92%8B\">王全璋</a></strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-thumbnail wp-image-602400\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/12/wangquanzhang-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/12/wangquanzhang-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/12/wangquanzhang-70x70.jpg 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/12/wangquanzhang-50x50.jpg 50w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/12/wangquanzhang.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></p>\n<ul class=\"st-related-posts\">\n<li><span class=\"related_date\">2018.12.27</span> <a title=\"彼得・达林：关于王全璋起诉书声明\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/12/by-%e5%bd%bc%e5%be%97%e3%83%bb%e8%be%be%e6%9e%97%ef%bc%9a%e5%85%b3%e4%ba%8e%e7%8e%8b%e5%85%a8%e7%92%8b%e8%b5%b7%e8%af%89%e4%b9%a6%e5%a3%b0%e6%98%8e/\">彼得・达林：关于王全璋起诉书声明</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"related_date\">2018.12.26</span> <a title=\"国际特赦组织：圣诞节前后审“敏感”案件成惯例 显示审判可疑  ‏\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/12/%e5%9b%bd%e9%99%85%e7%89%b9%e8%b5%a6%e7%bb%84%e7%bb%87%ef%bc%9a%e5%9c%a3%e8%af%9e%e8%8a%82%e5%89%8d%e5%90%8e%e5%ae%a1%e6%95%8f%e6%84%9f%e6%a1%88%e4%bb%b6%e6%88%90%e6%83%af%e4%be%8b/\">国际特赦组织：圣诞节前后审“敏感”案件成惯例 显示审判可疑 ‏</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"related_date\">2018.12.26</span> <a title=\"【众人推】709王全璋案现场：天津二中院门前\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/12/%e3%80%90%e4%bc%97%e4%ba%ba%e6%8e%a8%e3%80%91709%e7%8e%8b%e5%85%a8%e7%92%8b%e6%a1%88%e7%8e%b0%e5%9c%ba%ef%bc%9a%e5%a4%a9%e6%b4%a5%e4%ba%8c%e4%b8%ad%e9%99%a2%e9%97%a8%e5%89%8d/\">【众人推】709王全璋案现场：天津二中院门前</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"related_date\">2018.12.26</span> <a title=\"德国之声 | 王全璋案秘密审理 庭外警察戒备森严\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/12/%e5%be%b7%e5%9b%bd%e4%b9%8b%e5%a3%b0-%e7%8e%8b%e5%85%a8%e7%92%8b%e6%a1%88%e7%a7%98%e5%af%86%e5%ae%a1%e7%90%86-%e5%ba%ad%e5%a4%96%e8%ad%a6%e5%af%9f%e6%88%92%e5%a4%87%e6%a3%ae%e4%b8%a5/\">德国之声 | 王全璋案秘密审理 庭外警察戒备森严</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"related_date\">2018.12.25</span> <a title=\"李文足与709律师被国保阻止去天津支持王全璋\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.n